## The Necromancer's Laboratory

An ancient necromancer in his sanctum, surrounded by undead guardians and dark rituals. Environmental hazards everywhere. Multiple ways to win beyond straight combat.

**The Necromancer:**
- Fragile personally (low Vitality)
- Powerful magic (high Momentum, dangerous spells)
- Environmental control (can trigger hazards, seal doors)

**The Undead:**
- 10+ skeletal warriors
- Don't break morale, don't feel fear
- Controlled by necromancer—destroy him and they collapse

**The Environment:**
- Ritual circles that explode if disrupted
- Shelves of volatile reagents
- Trapped doors and windows
- Phylactery hidden somewhere (he can't truly die without destroying it)

**How This Plays:** Area effects devastate undead. Smart players target the necromancer. Creative players use the environment. The phylactery creates a second objective.

